@startuml
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
skinparam monochrome true
title User Account State Transition

[*] --> Registered : User signs up

Registered --> EmailVerificationPending : Verification email sent

EmailVerificationPending --> Verified : Email confirmed
EmailVerificationPending --> Registered : Resend verification

Verified --> Active : Account activated

Active --> Suspended : Policy violation\nor admin action
Active --> Deactivated : User deletes account

Suspended --> Active : Suspension lifted
Suspended --> Deactivated : Admin permanently bans

Deactivated --> [*] : Account removed

Registered : Account created
Registered : Email not verified
Registered : Limited access

Active : Full access
Active : Can book services
Active : Can make payments

Suspended : Temporary restriction
Suspended : Cannot login
Suspended : Cannot book

Deactivated : Account disabled
Deactivated : Data may be retained
Deactivated : Cannot be recovered

@enduml
